In the MATTER OF the Expungement of B.K. (B.K. - Petitioner) C-786 September Term 2017
080606 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 21, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005592-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
